## Documentation & Communication
* **Architecture Diagrams**: Maintain up-to-date architecture diagrams showing system components and interactions.
* **Runbooks**: Create runbooks for common operational tasks and incident response procedures.
* **Change Logs**: Document infrastructure changes, including reasons and impact.
* **Onboarding**: Provide clear documentation for new team members to understand and work with the infrastructure.
* **Code Review**: Follow code review standards in [python-code-review-command.mdc](../commands/python-code-review-command.md) when reviewing infrastructure code.
